female (CRBALC0501): 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84">A</emphasis>
epigyne, ventral 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84">B</emphasis>
vulva, dorsal. Abbreviations, female genitalia: D - diverticulum, H - epigynal hoods, MS - median septum, S - spermatheca. Scale bars: 0.2 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
